    "In this instance, the generated answer is not only correct but also superior to the ground truth, as it integrates the information from another helpful sentence: \"The PPI group received intravenous esomeprazole 4 h before the EST and then every 12 h for 1 day, followed by high-dose oral esomeprazole for 10 days.\"",
    "However, both ROUGE-1 and BERTScore fail to label this correct answer due to a lack of overlapping words.",
    "In contrast, the GPT evaluator assigns a score of 0.85, acknowledging the reasonableness of the generated output.",
    "This outcome highlights the potential of the GPT evaluator that evaluating not merely the words but also meanings can offer a more authentic and accurate evaluation.",
    "We also found that GPT exhibits logical thought when evaluating the answer during development."
